---
import Stars from "../components/Stars.astro";
---

<section id="about"
  class="min-h-screen flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-10 md:py-24 lg:py-20"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-col md:gap-0 md:py-20 lg:flex-row lg:gap-5 lg:py-10">
    <div
      class="w-[350px] h-[470px] md:w-[400px] lg:w-[500px] flex items-center justify-center ">
      <div class="p-5 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
        <Stars />
        <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold glow-effect">
          ¡Nosotros ponemos la música <br class="md:hidden" />
           y ustedes el ambiente!
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl mt-5 mb-2">
          Con una rica mezcla de ritmos y estilos <br />
          nuestra música te hará bailar y vibrar.
        </p>
        <a
          href="#"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
          class="text-white text-xl
            border-[3px] border-white rounded-full
            px-4 py-2 mt-10 hover:bg-white hover:text-black
            transition-colors duration-300"
          >Agenda tu fecha</a
        >
        <p class="text-white text-2xl mt-10 font-bold">¡No te vas a arrepentir!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-auto h-[370px] md:w-full md:h-[450px] lg:w-[550px] lg:h-[450px] felx flex-col items-center justify-center">
      <div class="mt-0 flex items-center justify-center">
        <div class="glow-effect-1 w-[230px] h-[250px] md:w-[400px] md:h-[370px] lg:w-[400px] lg:h-[380px]"></div>
        <img
          src="members.avif"
          alt="Miembros del grupo F-5"
          class="mt-0 rounded-4xl z-20 w-auto h-[300px] md:h-[410px] lg:h-[450px]"
        />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
